38#ifndef __HPROP_H__
39#define __HPROP_H__
40
41#include "headers.h"
42
43struct prop_data{
44 krb5_context context;
45 krb5_auth_context auth_context;
46 int sock;
47};
48
49#define HPROP_VERSION "hprop-0.0"
50#define HPROP_NAME "hprop"
51#define HPROP_KEYTAB "HDBGET:"
52#define HPROP_PORT 754
53
54#ifndef NEVERDATE
55#define NEVERDATE ((1U << 31) - 1)
56#endif
57
58krb5_error_code v5_prop(krb5_context, HDB*, hdb_entry_ex*, void*);
59int mit_prop_dump(void*, const char*);
60
61struct v4_principal {
62 char name[64];
63 char instance[64];
64 DES_cblock key;
65 int kvno;
66 int mkvno;
67 time_t exp_date;
68 time_t mod_date;
69 char mod_name[64];
70 char mod_instance[64];
71 int max_life;
72};
73
74int v4_prop(void*, struct v4_principal*);
75int v4_prop_dump(void *arg, const char*);
76
77#endif /* __HPROP_H__ */
